# API Conventions

- Generated GraphQL types and operations live in `api/generated/` — **never edit by hand**.
  Regenerate with `npm run generate` (`graphql-codegen --config codegen.yml`).
- Hand-written hooks that wrap generated operations live in `api/graphql-hooks.ts`.
  Add new hooks there; prefer a thin wrapper over calling `graphqlRequest` in components.
- Before regenerating the schema, **ask the user to enable Strapi develop mode** —
  introspection is disabled in production.
